        <abstract> 
<p>CD cannot swallow continental extensions. Has written to Lyell giving a lengthy criticism of the concept [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">1910</hi>] and has asked Lyell to forward the letter to JDH.</p>  
<p>Perhaps <hi rend="italic">Aristolochia</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Viscum</hi> are protandrous.</p> 
        </abstract>
